days for the new DLS group and 99 days for the conventional DLS group, revealing 
a significant difference between devices. There was, however, no significant 
difference in median patency time between the new DLS and the uncovered SEMS 
(198 days versus 344 days). Conclusion. The new DLS is efficient and safe and 
may be considered the first choice for unresectable distal malignant obstruction 
in cases with short life expectancy.

